{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a30084f716","title":"中央首长对湖南军方代表谈话摘要","origin":"周良霄、顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》, 2009。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d18b61999e","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"a30084f716"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"440b5f1bc1","name":"黄永胜","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"dce00e6de9","name":"湖南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"},{"id":"9fb3845f99","name":"黄永胜"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2b7b37cd10","type":"title","text":"中央首长对湖南军方代表谈话摘要","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"a6b906d3c4","type":"authors","text":"周恩来陈伯达黄永胜","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"1dc08d7eb0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：龙书金你认识了错误没有？","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"eb2d31b37b","type":"paragraph","text":"龙书金(湖南军区司令员)：我认识了。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"0498837761","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你认识什么？还没认识好。哪个叫刘子云？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"6c0ce76e48","type":"paragraph","text":"刘子云(湖南军区副司令员)：(站起来说)我叫刘子云。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"7564ea42b4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是那一派的，是“高司”派的吗？","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"e9806f5f4b","type":"paragraph","text":"刘子云：我不是。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"db68583543","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：明明你是“高司”派，怎么不是呢？“工联”你不支持，支持“高司”干坏事。崔琳来了没有？","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"03bfdb7a89","type":"paragraph","text":"崔琳(军区政治部副主任)来了。我叫崔琳。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"0bf8754b50","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是那一派的？","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"11688cc4d7","type":"paragraph","text":"崔琳：(未答)","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"b3d9c175ef","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：龙书金，你们军区搞的“湘江风雷”材料很不落实，是假的，欺骗中央，欺骗我，犯了错误还不承认，那还行吗？","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"d02c5952a8","type":"paragraph","text":"黄永胜(广州军区司令员)：你们给广州军区的报告材料也扩大了。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"35d6e83473","type":"paragraph","text":"龙书金：我一点不知道，是崔琳调查的，是崔琳搞的。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"d69ba8e951","type":"paragraph","text":"刘顺文(长沙政治干校校长)：你们犯了错误，现在还不老实承认，还你推我我推你。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"d9cc1761cd","type":"paragraph","text":"黎原(47军军长)：现在长沙武斗还继续发展，而且越来越严重，你们军区警备司令部不制止武斗，我们47军出面，请你们军区站出来的领导干部参加。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"c0e86fdf81","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：龙书金，谁叫你训练“高司”武工队的？谁叫你煽动农民进城的，你打算把毛主席的故乡的文化革命搞成什么样子？","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"dd61a822bd","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：真不像话！","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"bd37615fb8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你要好好检查错误。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"7a9cc28d54","type":"paragraph","text":"龙书金：我一定检查错误。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"},{"id":"c24523c11d","type":"paragraph","text":"黄永胜：我明天要走了，家里事很忙，湖南军区犯了方向性、路线性错误是肯定的。这次来北京，总理给你们的楼梯，叫你们下楼，如果你们的错误不好好检查的话，我看你们是回不去的。现在长沙还在死人，还在开枪。我明天就走，希望你们好好检查自己的错误，不然就不好办了。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716"}],"page":{"id":"214cd25159","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"a30084f716","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}